   "Reach L2: encrypt/decrypt a file with GPG; sign and verify a document.",
   "Reach L3: generate a TLS certificate and explain the handshake and certificate chain validation.",
   "Reach L4: implement AES-CBC and AES-GCM in Python; explain why GCM provides authenticated encryption.",
