   howTo:"ILR milestones from survival to professional proficiency. Mandarin requires 2,200+ hours to reach ILR 3 for English speakers. Characters and tones must be learned simultaneously from day one. Use Anki decks (HSK), HelloChinese or ChinesePod, and a tutor for tones.",
