   "Reach L2: form complete sentences on familiar topics and follow slow, clear Mandarin.",
   "Reach L3: sustain conversations on familiar topics; read basic simplified characters.",
   "Reach L4: understand main ideas at normal native speed; handle everyday tasks.",
