   advance:["Reach L1: 10-mile ruck at mission load without blisters or breakdown.","Reach L2: foot toughening — progressive mileage without blistering.","Reach L3: heat acclimatization in 90°F+.","Reach L4: cold tolerance at 20°F or below.","Reach L5: 10+ hours demanding work without failure.","Reach L6: 12-mile ruck at combat load.","Reach L7: 48 hours sustained effort.","Reach L8: mission-capable under any conditions."],
