   levels:[
     "Map a real or simulated attack to the cyber kill chain; identify where detection/disruption could occur","Research a named threat actor using only open sources; produce a targeting profile","Write a mission planning order for a notional cyber operation using Army doctrinal format","Identify the legal authorities required for a specific cyber action; document the ROE limitations","Brief a cyber operation plan to a notional O-4 commander; field questions","Conduct a tabletop exercise where your team must plan a defensive cyber operation under time pressure","Plan and execute a full offensive/defensive cyber exercise using doctrinal format from start to after-action","Synchronize a cyber element with a conventional maneuver plan (joint planning exercise or simulation)"],
