   advance:["Reach L1: net worth tracked.","Reach L2: budget 3 months.","Reach L3: emergency fund intact.","Reach L4: high-interest debt gone.","Reach L5: TSP + BRS.","Reach L6: taxes optimized.","Reach L7: investing automated.","Reach L8: 10-year plan.","Reach L9: all tax-advantaged accounts.","Reach L10: retirement modeled.","Reach L11: financial autopilot."],
